about.summary: CoffeeScript is a little language that compiles into JavaScript

name: rb-coffee-script-source
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "coffee-script-source" %}
{% set version = "1.12.2" %}

package:
  name: rb-{{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://rubygems.org/downloads/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.gem
  sha256: e12b16fd8927fbbf8b87cb2e9a85a6cf457c6881cc7ff8b1af15b31f70da07a4

build:
  noarch: generic
  number: 0
  script:
    - gem install -N -l -V --norc --ignore-dependencies {{ name }}-{{ version }}.gem
  skip: {{ win }}

requirements:
  host:
    - ruby
  run:
    - ruby

test:
  commands:
    - gem list -i {{ name }} -v {{ version }}

about:
  home: https://rubygems.org/gems/{{ name }}
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: CoffeeScript is a little language that compiles into JavaScript

  doc_url: https://www.rubydoc.info/gems/{{ name }}

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - sodre
